headline: Principal Financial (PFG) Reports Q3 Earnings: What Key Metrics Have to Say
summary: While the top- and bottom-line numbers for Principal Financial (PFG) give a sense of how the business performed in the quarter ended September 2025, it could be worth looking at how some of its key metrics compare to Wall Street estimates and year-ago values.

headline: Principal Financial: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa (AP) — Principal Financial Group Inc. PFG) on Monday reported third-quarter net income of $213.8 million. On a per-share basis, the Des Moines, Iowa-based company said it had profit of 95 cents.
